尺寸上似乎比 JBL 在这个范围内的较小选择稍微更好地平衡。</p><p>如果你想要一款价格低于 400 美元、比一般便携式设备更热情、但仍具有 IP67 防风雨性能的产品，那么这很容易成为你的最爱。它具有足够的输出，可以为小型晚会或后院的悬挂带来活力，尽管它的声音很大，但最好是在附近或室内，这样低音可以充分产生共鸣。</p><h3> UE Hyperboom（400 美元）</h3><p><core-commerce id="f4a9907d84aa4de1aecae9e87300470c" data-type="product-list"></p><p><strong>蓝牙：</strong> 5.0<br><strong>电池寿命：</strong>长达 24 小时<br><strong>防护等级：</strong> IPX4<br><strong>辅助输入：</strong> 3.5mm，光纤<br><strong>频率范围：</strong> 45Hz - 20kHz<br><strong>应用程序：</strong>是的</p><p><a data-i13n="cpos:15;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiI2NmVhNTY3YS1jOTg3LTRjMmUtYTJmZi0wMjkwNGVmZGU2ZWEiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYW1hem9uLmNvbS9VbHRpbWF0ZS1FYXJzLUhZUEVSQk9PTS1CbHVldG9vdGgtUmVzaXN0YW50L2RwL0IwN1hKOEI5TlY_dGFnPWdkZ3QwYy1wLW8tZngtMjAiLCJjb250ZW50VXVpZCI6IjFiZDNhMGJkLTdjYTEtNDU0Yi1iNGNkLTNhZmE1NWQ1MTg1MCJ9&amp;signature=AQAAAcNPWM_l7hxPWF-aYRZXZ91RJxfAs4e8ofyC7kxRbG7Z&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FUltimate-Ears-HYPERBOOM-Bluetooth-Resistant%2Fdp%2FB07XJ8B9NV">UE Hyperboom</a>是一款全能型产品，具有美观、便携、丰富的连接选项以及响亮而有力的输出（尽管是压缩的）。技术织物外观（现在包括白色选项）让它生活在您的家具中，而不会尖叫“派对盒”，而光纤输入则提供了可能的电视扬声器替代方案。顶部的大电容按钮可以让任何人调节音量、暂停或播放音乐，并从两个并发蓝牙连接或硬连线输入（3.5 毫米或光纤）中进行选择。硅胶提手的边缘有有线端口，一个用于为 USB 设备充电，另一个用于供电。 Hyperboom 的电池续航时间预计可达 24 小时，而且待机状态下也能保持电量。</p><p>只要派对的首要关注点是保真度，这款功能强大且响亮（大约 100dB）的扬声器就会令大多数人满意。使用 UE 应用程序远程打开或关闭设备电源的能力也是一个受欢迎的功能。此外，您还可以使用 PartyUp 功能轻松将声音扩展到其他 Ultimate Ears Boom 扬声器（Wonderboom 除外）。 IPX4 等级意味着一些溢出的饮料不会对其造成困扰，但它并不是全天候冒险的最佳蓝牙扬声器选择。</p><h3>马歇尔·塔夫顿（400 美元）</h3><p><core-commerce id="c2c455281697497496b888a10f494fc7" data-type="product-list"></p><p><strong>蓝牙：</strong> 5.0<br><strong>电池寿命：</strong>长达 20 小时<br><strong>防护等级：</strong> IPX2<br><strong>辅助输入：</strong> 3.5mm<br><strong>频率范围：</strong> 40Hz - 20kHz<br><strong>应用程序：</strong>没有</p><p>如果您不了解 Marshall 在放大器和摇滚音乐方面的历史，其设计应该会为您提供线索<a data-i13n="cpos:16;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAbo_J-etV12iBUMEXMg9O3ytZzhC3SAk-LnKuNV-o_d6&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FMarshall-Tufton-Portable-Bluetooth-Speaker%2Fdp%2FB07QJD5MT4">。Tufton</a>是该公司最大的<em>便携式</em>蓝牙扬声器，看起来很像放大器本身（大多数放大器都是如此）。它的顶部有物理旋钮和一条有助于移动它的背带。虽然它看起来像音乐会装备一样坚固，但它不像某些仅具有 IPX2 防护等级的产品那样不受环境影响，因此可以防止来自上方的光线溅射。</p><p>无论您是否是该品牌的粉丝，丰富而明显的震撼输出可能会让您成为其中之一。在聆听 Tufton 时，我们感到被声音所吸引，比我们在这个规模上测试的大多数其他扬声器都要强烈一些。它的音频表现是动态的、温暖的，而且我们敢说，是模拟的。它也是多向的，背面有一个补充驱动器和一个低音端口。</p><p>没有用于调整均衡器的应用程序，只有物理控件，包括蓝牙连接按钮、电源/音量旋钮以及两个低音和高音旋钮。开机后，您可以使用音量旋钮设置最大动态余量并从源动态调整音量。低音和高音旋钮可帮助您选择冒险的基调，从纯平的音景到增强的音景。我们只是希望您能在黑暗中看到表盘指示器。其他功能包括 aptX 支持和快速充电功能，只需 20 分钟即可提供 4 小时的聆听时间，并且具有出色的待机电池寿命。</p><h2><strong>价格：450 美元及以上</strong></h2><h3>JBL Boombox 3（500 美元）</h3><p><core-commerce id="3d53d17f1472443d9fdf4fa5bd99dc6a" data-type="product-list"></p><p><strong>蓝牙：</strong> 5.3<br><strong>电池寿命：</strong>长达 24 小时<br><strong>防护等级：</strong> IPX7<br><strong>辅助输入：</strong> 3.5mm<br><strong>频率范围：</strong> 40Hz - 20kHz<br><strong>应用程序：</strong>是的</p><p>如果您是 JBL 小型便携式设备的粉丝，但又想将音量调高几度， <a data-i13n="cpos:17;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiI2NmVhNTY3YS1jOTg3LTRjMmUtYTJmZi0wMjkwNGVmZGU2ZWEiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYW1hem9uLmNvbS9ncC9wcm9kdWN0L0IwOVlEUzhCSEs_dGFnPWdkZ3QwYy1wLW8tZngtMjAiLCJjb250ZW50VXVpZCI6IjFiZDNhMGJkLTdjYTEtNDU0Yi1iNGNkLTNhZmE1NWQ1MTg1MCJ9&amp;signature=AQAAAZpZJ5RN0EU4dauV-xJCkqxuAuWxZlqA1jluZeUyCyf5&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fgp%2Fproduct%2FB09YDS8BHK">Boombox 3</a>是一个不错的选择。这款 160 瓦以上的 Xtreme 3 兄弟提供了熟悉的 JBL 声音，但声音更大。输出具有明亮、动态的高音和地板震动的低音，这可能会从具有表面反射的室内环境中受益更多。它没有“扬声器”那样的长距离，但需要明确的是，它的声音相当大。这是一款适合您的地下室娱乐室、车库聚会、海滩或池畔疯狂的舞会工具。</p><p> Boombox 3 较上一代有一些升级。外观看起来基本相同，但现在的 IP67 等级使其非常坚固耐用。它还重了 14.7 磅，可能是因为该设备现在在中音和高音扬声器旁边配备了低音扬声器。</p><p>在大多数情况下，当您希望音乐成为节目的明星（或至少不消失在背景中）时，它仍然是一款方便的随身携带扬声器。电池可以让您玩长达 24 小时，而且在插入电源时也能以最大音量运行。事实上，当它连接到插座时，总输出瓦数会从 160 瓦提升到 180 瓦。</p><h3>索尼 SRS-XP700（约 398 美元）</h3><p><core-commerce id="cd16262743454b4ca679d1e717af5cee" data-type="product-list"></p><p><strong>蓝牙：</strong> 5.0<br><strong>电池寿命：</strong>长达 20 小时<br><strong>防护等级：</strong> IPX4<br><strong>辅助输入：</strong> 3.5 毫米、USB 拇指驱动器监听、吉他、麦克风<br><strong>频率范围：</strong>不适用<br><strong>应用程序：</strong>是的</p><p>索尼的大型<a data-i13n="cpos:18;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAdy6iMeOziUFDec3PsldvU2pdcJfYoVrxHmthKZk8dHR&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FSony-Portable-Bluetooth-Karaoke-Party-Speaker-Splash-Resistant-Hour-Battery%2Fdp%2FB094T99V63">SRS-XP700 蓝牙扬声器</a>是一款适合大声、重击节拍爱好者的聚会扬声器。该装置具有未来派立体声扬声器的外观，高 2.25 英尺，重约 37 磅，顶部和底部扶手的内部具有令人愉悦的灯光效果。您还可以找到 USB 充电端口和 LDAC 支持，同时该应用程序还提供包括灯光控制在内的定制功能。</p><p> The XP700 remains portable enough for many people to shuffle around locally without <em>too</em> much effort and its IPX4 rating means it can handle spills and splashes. The exterior is hard plastic with some rubberized feet, but it&#39;s not the type of speaker you want to treat carelessly. It&#39;s mostly a homebody that can fire up parties in lofts, garages, basements or backyards. You can also wirelessly pair two for a more powerful experience.</p><p> While the sound is big and bassy, it comes up short on handling the lowest registers well. Also, the high end isn&#39;t as pronounced as it could be, so it may not be for everyone. It&#39;s more of a loudspeaker style, so it&#39;s better in bigger rooms and shines at louder volumes.</p><h3> Soundboks Go ($699)</h3><p><core-commerce id="a0731d1938ed48e3ada7e9b7392dcdc8" data-type="product-list"></p><p><strong>蓝牙：</strong> 5.0<br> <strong>Battery life:</strong> Up to 40 hours<br> <strong>IP Rating:</strong> IP65<br><strong>辅助输入：</strong> 3.5mm<br> <strong>Frequency range:</strong> 40Hz - 20kHz<br><strong>应用程序：</strong>是的</p><p>The <a data-i13n="cpos:19;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiI2NmVhNTY3YS1jOTg3LTRjMmUtYTJmZi0wMjkwNGVmZGU2ZWEiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYW1hem9uLmNvbS9ncC9wcm9kdWN0L0IwOVlSTVJHS1Y_dGFnPWdkZ3QwYy1wLW8tZngtMjAiLCJjb250ZW50VXVpZCI6IjFiZDNhMGJkLTdjYTEtNDU0Yi1iNGNkLTNhZmE1NWQ1MTg1MCJ9&amp;signature=AQAAAVR6IRJRQbNa62mA9zIUHt7c2_oKphMrHKHo9U5-R4d1&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fgp%2Fproduct%2FB09YRMRGKV">Soundboks Go</a> is a top performer if you&#39;re looking for a portable Bluetooth option that provides a big sound for larger spaces, although it comes at a price. This unpretentious black rectangle is half the size of its more professional sibling the Soundboks Gen 3. It packs one 10-inch woofer and a 1-inch domed tweeter, both powered by two 72W RMS amps for massive sound and chunky bass, even at a distance.</p><p> At 20 pounds, this party speaker is fairly easy to lug around and looks about the size of carry-on luggage. You can even get the optional shoulder strap, which helps for longer missions. It has a flexible TPE handle on top, silicone bumpers around the edges and ABS+Polycarbonate exterior and grill. The IP65 rating also marks it as a resilient device in most environments.</p><p> The sound makes a big statement here. Output levels are rated at up to 121dB, with clear mids and highs projecting clearly across large areas. The low end also has a significant presence at a distance, matching up with 40Hz frequency response. It&#39;s definitely capable enough to support large gatherings.</p><p> The speaker is easy to connect to via Bluetooth and the partner app offers EQ customization, audio profiles and OTA firmware updates. There&#39;s a solitary 3.5mm stereo input on the Go, but its wireless expansion shines, letting you connect up to five Soundboks Gen 3 or Go speakers at the touch of a button with its built-in SKAA wireless support.</p><p> Lastly, the battery pack is removable, swappable and also long-lasting for a speaker this size; at low to mid volume, it&#39;s rated at up to 40 hours runtime. For transparency, Soundboks also lets you know to expect around 10 hours of play at full volume. You <em>can</em> also run this while charging, but there are strict warnings about keeping the volume low while doing so (it&#39;s not recommended unless you&#39;re desperate).</p><h2>常见问题解答</h2><h3>How does a Bluetooth speaker work?</h3><p> Bluetooth technology lets devices connect and exchange data over short distances using ultra high frequency (UHF) radio waves. It&#39;s the frequency range that&#39;s carved out for industrial, scientific and medical purposes, called the 2.4GHz ISM spectrum band. This range is available worldwide, making it easy for companies to use with devices for global markets.</p><p> Bluetooth speakers include this tech, which lets them communicate with source devices like smartphones, tablets or computers in order to exchange data. The two devices pair by sharing a unique code and will work within the proscribed range for the device and Bluetooth version.</p><p> Ever since Bluetooth 4.0 was released over a decade ago, new iterations usually improve on range, use less power and offer expanded connectivity with features like multipoint (allowing more than one device to be connected at the same time, for instance).</p><h3> Who should buy a Portable Bluetooth speaker?</h3><p> If you want to play music while you&#39;re out-and-about on something other than headphones, a portable Bluetooth speaker is probably what you want. There&#39;s a broad range of devices for all types of circumstances. Many adventurous people will want a relatively lightweight portable that&#39;s rugged enough to handle the elements while also packing enough charge to play for hours on end. Others may simply need a speaker they can move around the house or use in the backyard. In this case, you can choose larger less rugged models that may offer better sound.</p> This article originally appeared on Engadget at https://www.engadget.com/best-portable-bluetooth-speakers-133004551.html?src=rss]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/best-portable-bluetooth-speakers-133004551.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> 1bd3a0bd-7ca1-454b-b4cd-3afa55d51850</guid><dc:creator> Jon Turi</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher> Engadget</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder> Engadget</dc:rightsholder><pubDate> Fri, 21 Jul 2023 12:08:06 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1689941287</ingested><modified> 2023-07-21T12:08:22+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[Speakers & Headphones]]></category><category><![CDATA[Audio Technology]]></category><category><![CDATA[Technology & Electronics]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Jon Turi]]></category><media:content height="1615" medium="image" url="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2022-04/85e08920-b759-11ec-beb9-015235c0a851" width="2500"><media:keywords> headline </media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><